OL,3,C'Emotional' reunion for father and son
OL,4,Ckept apart for over a decade
OL,6,FA prisoner given a controversial
OL,7,FImprisonment for Public Protection
OL,8,F(IPP) sentence has finally met his son
OL,9,Fafter being denied access for more
OL,10,Fthan a decade.
OL,12,FThomas White, from Bury, is one of
OL,13,Fnearly 3,000 prisoners locked up under
OL,14,Fthe now defunct law, which sets a
OL,15,Fminimum but not a maximum term in
OL,16,Fprison.
