OL,3,C'Emotional' reunion for father and son
OL,4,Ckept apart for over a decade
OL,6,FNow after 10 years of campaigning,
OL,7,FThomas has finally been allowed to
OL,8,Fmeet his son Kayden, whom he last saw
OL,9,Fas a baby, in what has been described
OL,10,Fas a 'very emotional' reunion.
OL,12,FKayden White is now 14-years-old and
OL,13,Fsays when he finally got to meet his
OL,14,Ffather, it was 'dead emotional'.
OL,16,F"Everyone was just crying," he said.
OL,17,F"My nana was bawling her eyes out, the
OL,18,Fsocial worker was crying - it was all
OL,19,Fdead emotional.
OL,21,F"I also shed a few tears."
