OL,3,C'Emotional' reunion for father and son
OL,4,Ckept apart for over a decade
OL,6,Fafter being convicted of street
OL,7,Frobbery after stealing a mobile phone
OL,8,Fduring a night out.
OL,10,FHe has been in prison ever since.
OL,12,FIPP sentences were abolished in 2012,
OL,13,Fhowever many prisoners like Thomas are
OL,14,Fstill imprisoned under the sentence.
OL,16,FIt was only after a recent
OL,17,Fintervention from Lord David Blunkett
OL,18,F(who introduced IPPs in 2005) that the
OL,19,Ffamily were helped to gain visiting
OL,20,Fpermissions for the father and son.
