OL,3,C'Emotional' reunion for father and son
OL,4,Ckept apart for over a decade
OL,6,FThomas has now been diagnosed with
OL,7,Fparanoid schizophrenia, and his family
OL,8,Fbelieve the probable cause for that is
OL,9,Fthe hopelessness of never knowing if
OL,10,Fhe will ever be released.
OL,12,FKayden told ITV's Granada Reports he
OL,13,Ffeels angry it has taken this long to
OL,14,Fallow him to meet his dad.
OL,16,F"I just hope no other child has to go
OL,17,Fthrough what I did. It shouldn't have
OL,18,Ftaken so long - it is not right," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
