OL,3,C'Emotional' reunion for father and son
OL,4,Ckept apart for over a decade
OL,6,FThe family are calling for Thomas to
OL,7,Fbe moved to a mental health
OL,8,Finstitution.
OL,10,FMeanwhile pressure is growing on the
OL,11,FUK Government and the Justice Minister
OL,12,FAlex Chalk to review IPPs as a matter
OL,13,Fof urgency.
OL,15,F90 suicides have been recorded by
OL,16,Fprisoners on IPPs since 2005, making
OL,17,Fthem twice as likely than other
OL,18,Fprisoners to take their own lives.
