OL,3,C'Emotional' reunion for father and son
OL,4,Ckept apart for over a decade
OL,6,FThe Prison Governors' Union has
OL,7,Fdescribed IPPs as 'the blot on our
OL,8,Flegal system', whilst a senior coroner
OL,9,Fsaid they were 'inhumane and
OL,10,Findefensible' and warned they would
OL,11,Fkill more if the Government doesn't
OL,12,Fact fast.
OL,14,FIt comes as the Lords are due to vote
OL,15,Fon crucial IPP amendments to the
OL,16,FVictims and Prisoners Bill in May 2024.
