OL,3,C'Emotional' reunion for father and son
OL,4,Ckept apart for over a decade
OL,6,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We have reduced the number of
OL,8,Funreleased IPP prisoners by three-
OL,9,Fquarters since we scrapped the
OL,10,Fsentence in 2012, but retrospectively
OL,11,Fchanging sentences poses a risk to
OL,12,Fpublic safety because offenders who
OL,13,Fthe Parole Board have deemed unsafe
OL,14,Ffor release, many of whom have
OL,15,Fcommitted serious violent or sexual
OL,16,Foffences, would leave prison without
OL,17,Fprobation supervision and support.
